{"tid":372009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話你知﹕澳狗八成半供電靠內地","createTime":"2017-08-24T05:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T07:40:57.000Z","uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b29a0f8b2a2e3e262328332bb3e7a700ddb8edb","tid":372009,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】澳門電力指現時澳門八成半電力由內地供應，昨天中午珠海向澳供電線路故障，一度引致全澳門停電。澳門立法會議員區錦新表示，事件反映澳門本地發電比例偏低，一旦遇事即停電，呼籲增加本地發電比例。<br />\n澳電倡建天然氣發電機組未獲批<br />\n<br />\n區錦新說，澳門電力年前建議興建天然氣發電機組，但不獲政府批准，希望經今次事件後盡快通過建議。<br />\n澳門電力網頁顯示，澳門的輸電網包括22座主變電站及6座客戶高壓開關站及高壓電纜。電網通過兩個110千伏聯絡通道和兩個220千伏聯絡通道和中國南方電網互聯。<br />\n本港環團「350香港」聯絡主任古偉牧表示，本港電力公司有充裕機組向本港供電，料不會出現澳門同類嚴重情况，但事件反映不能太依賴單一供電來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170824/s00001/1503510275636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170824%2Fs00001%2F1503510275636&d=5u6NhZoHHrEugB6bWmFGsaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=7b6f8f90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170824%2Fs00001%2F1503510275636&h=968eea35\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170824/s00001/1503510275636</a>"},{"pid":"ea034496ab510001502591a863162f92603f6abe","tid":372009,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"話澳門聽話所以繁榮果班老野點兜好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b78f1f4c2f91d9ee78965265ff3f16dbd656a7","tid":372009,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:08:26.000Z","msg":"內地？"},{"pid":"221fcec9cddf5ac7186cb6b9c40d390e89b187ee","tid":372009,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內地？</blockquote><br />\n澳門嘅內地咪珠海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無錯喎"},{"pid":"0a